          </button>
          <div class="bnj-reel__overlay"></div>
          <div class="bnj-reel__label">Story 01</div>
        </div>

        <div class="bnj-reel" data-bnj-reel>
          <video
            class="bnj-reel__video"
            preload="auto"
            playsinline
            muted
            loop
            autoplay
            data-bnj-reel-el
          >
            <source src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/266f09cc6ff4446a9365a35ec448c594.mp4" type="video/mp4">
          </video>
          <button class="bnj-reel__play" aria-label="Play story" data-bnj-reel-trigger>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="bnj-reel__overlay"></div>
          <div class="bnj-reel__label">Story 02</div>
        </div>

        <div class="bnj-reel" data-bnj-reel>
          <video
            class="bnj-reel__video"
            preload="auto"
            playsinline
            muted
            loop
            autoplay
            data-bnj-reel-el
          >
            <source src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/d9097f8d52ad448d88f21a106764a8c2.mp4" type="video/mp4">
          </video>
          <button class="bnj-reel__play" aria-label="Play story" data-bnj-reel-trigger>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="bnj-reel__overlay"></div>
          <div class="bnj-reel__label">Story 03</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% comment %} ============ PILLARS ============ {% endcomment %}
  <section class="bnj-pillars">
    <div class="bnj-container">
      <div class="bnj-section-header">
        <div class="bnj-eyebrow bnj-eyebrow--center">What We Stand For</div>
        <h2 class="bnj-section-headline">
          THREE THINGS WE<br>
          <span class="bnj-italic">Never</span> COMPROMISE ON.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="bnj-pillars__grid">
        <div class="bnj-pillar">
          <div class="bnj-pillar__num">01 / Quality</div>
          <h3>Built To Last More Than One Season.</h3>
          <p>Premium fabrics. Construction details that survive the gym, the wash cycle, and the years. We build for athletes who wear their gear into the ground, not for closets that need refilling every quarter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bnj-pillar">
          <div class="bnj-pillar__num">02 / Story</div>
          <h3>Born From Real Athletic Programs.</h3>
          <p>Every piece carries the DNA of the camps, clubs, and athletes we work with. This isn't a brand inventing community. It's a brand that started inside one and decided to dress it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bnj-pillar">
          <div class="bnj-pillar__num">03 / Community</div>
          <h3>For The Family. For The Work.</h3>
          <p>We make custom apparel for clubs, schools, and grassroots teams. We support the programs that built us. When you wear Blessed, you wear something tied to people putting in the work alongside you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% comment %} ============ EDITORIAL FULL BLEED ============ {% endcomment %}
  <section class="bnj-fullbleed" style="background-image: url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0726/4210/1338/files/anelissaphoto-38.jpg?v=1777654998');">
    <div class="bnj-fullbleed__overlay"></div>
    <div class="bnj-fullbleed__inner">
      <div class="bnj-eyebrow bnj-eyebrow--center">Sport. Streets. Life.</div>
      <h2 class="bnj-fullbleed__headline">
        FROM THE COURT.<br>
        <span class="bnj-italic">To The</span> CONCRETE.
      </h2>
      <p class="bnj-fullbleed__text">Born in basketball. Built for everywhere the work takes you. Blessed lives between the gym, the streets, and the in between.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% comment %} ============ EDITORIAL QUOTE ============ {% endcomment %}
  <section class="bnj-quote" style="background-image: url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0726/4210/1338/files/2_7_ba985e6c-22d8-4abc-8aa8-cb91e9caa224.png?v=1777629599');">
